## Requirements
- Tape hiss: pink noise low-passed at 8kHz, gain 0.08, always present when tape loaded
- Static crackle: random clicks/pops at low rate (~2-4 per second)
## Acceptance Criteria
- Tape hiss always audible when VCR has tape
- Crackle sounds random and natural
- Both stop when tape ejected